        ### [HDC](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/HDC.md)

        A message format used for describing a currency based on OpenPGP and Universal Dividend.

        > Allow currency description

        #### It defines 3 documents:

        * Public Keys for cryptography features
        * Amendments for describing currency & members
        * Transactions for exchanging coins

