        ### [Network](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/Network.md)

        A message format for allowing to manage HDC data over a distributed uCoin network.

        > Allow currency decentralization

        #### It defines 4 documents:

        * Peer document for peer's description
        * Forward document for routing transactions
        * Status document to know peers' current state
        * Wallet document to allow coins' distribution

