        ### [Registry](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/Registry.md)

        A message format & protocol *on top of* UCP, allowing for automated evolution of a uCoin currency.

        > Allow currency automation

        #### Its goal is to:

        * Automated acceptation of new members
        * Automated voting of the Contract
        * Allow for democratic changing of the monetary rules

