        ### [HTTP API](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/HTTP_API.md)

        The first existing API implementing both [HDC](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/HDC.md) + 
        [Network](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/Network.md) + 
        [Registry](https://github.com/ucoin-io/ucoin/blob/master/doc/Registry.md) over simple HTTP GET/POST methods.

        #### Special features:

        * Security & synchronization through Merkle trees
        * Implementing HKP protocol (PKS server)
        * JSON responses
